    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle is a standout example of meticulous ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its accident-free history. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats remain firm with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it has never been smoked in. All onboard technology\u2014including the infotainment system, climate control, and driver-assist features\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak form, supported by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every oil change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of corrosion or leaks. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey, investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
